
	- Create project
	- Install necessary packages (Asp.Net)
	- Create Models
	- Create DbContext Subclass (Asp.Net)
	- Migrate Database
	------------------------------------------------------
	
	- Create controllers
	- Map Routes
	
	Laravel has no POPO classes
	
	C	-	create
	R	-	index
	U	-	update
	D	-	destroy
	
	
	index()		-	list all 
	create()	-	form to create
	store()		-	save a new resource
	show()		-	list single
	edit()		-	form to edit
	update()	-	update existing resource
	destroy()	-	delete a resource
	
	The job of controller is to respond to request.
	
	<form action="/question" method="">
	
	</form>
	
	http://127.0.0.1:8000/question
	
	200	=	OK
	404	=	Not Found
	500	=	Server Internal Error

